Title: Teeter
Description: ['Keina Suda\'s 1st EP titled "teeter" will have a limited edition release bundled with a DVD that contains 2 animated items on December 16, 2019. First is the official music video for ', mock, " animated by Avogado6 (a short version was also released on Suda's official YouTube channel). Second is the official music video for ", Dolly, " animated by Avogado6 (it was also released on Suda's official YouTube channel)."]
